This application is hosted at Heroku Garden: http://etvnet.heroku.com

= Etvnet Seek -- Command line tool for getting mms urls from etvnet service.

= Installing Etvnet Sinatra Application and command line utility

== Installing the Gem
    $ sudo gem sources -a http://gemcutter.org
    $ sudo gem install etvnet

== Usage

Usage: etvnet-seek [options] keywords
    -s, --search                     Display Search Menu
    -t, --translit                   Enter russian keywords in translit
    -b, --best-hunred                Display Best 100 Menu
    -n, --new_items                  Display New Items Menu
    -p, --premier                    Display Premier of the Week Menu
    -c, --channels                   Display Channels Menu
    -a, --catalog                    Display Catalog Menu
    -m, --main                       Display Main Menu
    -h, --help                       Display this screen


Usage: etvnet - to start sinatra application